<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<template>
    <role>Location Scene Generator</role>
    
    <systemPrompt>
You are a specialized prompt generator for creating fantasy RPG location scene images.

Location Information:
Name/ID: {{ locationId }}
Description: 
    {{ locationDescription | replace('\n', '\n    ') }}
Base Level: {{ locationBaseLevel }}

{% if locationExits %}
Available Exits:
{% for direction, exit in locationExits %}
- {{ direction }}: {{ exit.description or 'An unexplored passage' }}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}
    </systemPrompt>
    
    <imagePrompt>
Create an image prompt in 1 to 4 paragraphs of prose for the following.

Scene Description: 
    {{ locationDescription | replace('\n', '\n    ') }}

Environmental Details Based on Level:
{% if locationBaseLevel <= 3 %}
- Peaceful, well-maintained area with safe pathways
- Gentle lighting, welcoming atmosphere
- Signs of civilization or friendly inhabitants
{% elif locationBaseLevel <= 7 %}
- Moderately challenging terrain with some hazards
- Balanced lighting with areas of shadow and light
- Mix of natural and civilized elements
{% elif locationBaseLevel <= 12 %}
- Dangerous, foreboding landscape
- Dramatic lighting with deep shadows
- Wild, untamed environment with visible threats
{% else %}
- Extremely perilous, otherworldly terrain
- Ominous, supernatural lighting effects
- Hostile environment with epic scale dangers
{% endif %}

Visual Style Guidelines:
- Fantasy RPG environment concept art
- Atmospheric perspective with depth
- Rich environmental storytelling
- Immersive world-building details

Technical Specifications:
Camera: Wide establishing shot showing the full environment
Perspective: Ground level view as an adventurer would see it
Depth of Field: Sharp foreground with atmospheric background

{% if locationExits %}
Composition: Include visible pathways or passages leading {{ locationExits | list | join(', ') }}
{% else %}
Composition: Self-contained environment with clear boundaries
{% endif %}

Lighting: 
{% if locationBaseLevel <= 5 %}
Natural, welcoming light that highlights safe travel routes
{% else %}
Dramatic, moody lighting that emphasizes danger and mystery
{% endif %}

Art Style: High-quality fantasy environment art, detailed location scene, professional digital matte painting, fantasy RPG world concept art

Mood: 
{% if locationBaseLevel <= 3 %}
Peaceful and inviting, safe haven atmosphere
{% elif locationBaseLevel <= 7 %}
Adventurous and mysterious, moderate danger
{% elif locationBaseLevel <= 12 %}
Ominous and challenging, clear danger signals
{% else %}
Epic and terrifying, legendary-level threats
{% endif %}

Quality Tags: masterpiece, best quality, highly detailed, fantasy environment, RPG location art, professional concept art, atmospheric scene, environmental storytelling
    </imagePrompt>
</template>